1115
01:51:01,148 --> 01:51:04,589
This ordinance is not happening in a vacuum.

1116
01:51:05,189 --> 01:51:05,869
We have,

1117
01:51:08,160 --> 01:51:12,628
a federal threat against people in our community.

1118
01:51:15,112 --> 01:51:20,902
I think we all, or some of us, maybe not all of us, but some of us,

1119
01:51:22,034 --> 01:51:25,076
are committed to protecting our neighbors.

1120
01:51:25,856 --> 01:51:33,922
We're not gonna let them get swept up and put in concentration camps and deported from our community.

1121
01:51:34,602 --> 01:51:44,028
We are not going to put up with the local police cooperating with the federal authorities to take people out of our community.

1122
01:51:44,408 --> 01:51:46,169
