1131
01:52:18,098 --> 01:52:21,804
You think first about the money and second about the people.

1132
01:52:23,390 --> 01:52:27,593
That really, I'd like to use a curse word, but I won't.

1133
01:52:28,134 --> 01:52:32,157
But I mean, that type of thinking is just archaic.

1134
01:52:33,138 --> 01:52:40,464
And one time I said about some people in the city, including you, George, that you were a relic of another alien.

