Eileen, please direct your comments to the chair, and I'm gonna have to give Councilor Scarpelli a chance to respond.

1136
01:52:45,768 --> 01:52:47,009
Please direct your comments to the chair.

1137
01:52:49,891 --> 01:52:50,752
Councilor Scarpelli.

1138
01:52:52,116 --> 01:52:54,518
I know this is so people realize Ms.

1139
01:52:54,558 --> 01:52:56,759
Lerner has called me a racist for many, many years.

1140
01:52:57,679 --> 01:53:00,101
I'm a first-generation American.

1141
01:53:00,501 --> 01:53:02,022
My parents are immigrants from Italy.

1142
01:53:02,622 --> 01:53:07,425
They came across legally and did exactly what had to be done.

1143
01:53:08,206 --> 01:53:11,448
They love this country, and they raised a proud American.

1144
01:53:13,089 --> 01:53:16,011
I worked in a community that's very diverse, Mr. President.

1145
01:53:17,372 --> 01:53:17,912
Unlike Ms.

1146
01:53:17,972 --> 01:53:21,234
Lerner, I've sat in a living room with an ICE agent.

1147
01:53:22,012 --> 01:53:25,153
and a family of illegal members.

1148
01:53:27,713 --> 01:53:29,233
And I understand the situation.

1149
01:53:30,033 --> 01:53:33,194
But we just had two human rights members just say what?

1150
01:53:34,754 --> 01:53:35,734
They've worked with the chief.

1151
01:53:36,354 --> 01:53:38,815
We've had the existing plan in place for five and a half years.

1152
01:53:39,395 --> 01:53:40,475
It's worked amazingly.

1153
01:53:41,735 --> 01:53:47,816
This is what was mentioned last time where people are missing, when Mr. Lerner's talking about money.

1154
01:53:49,017 --> 01:53:50,877
My fear at the time was understanding

1155
01:53:52,128 --> 01:54:02,855
with the city of Medford and where we are financially, is what are the financial ramifications if there is negative feedback from the federal government?

1156
01:54:03,955 --> 01:54:06,096
