1157
01:54:07,257 --> 01:54:10,979
Well, in Cambridge, in Boston, in Somerville, they can survive.

1158
01:54:11,900 --> 01:54:13,781
In Medford, I question if we can.

1159
01:54:14,782 --> 01:54:18,064
And that's our basic necessities, police, fire, school.

1160
01:54:20,485 --> 01:54:21,506
That was my concern.

1161
01:54:22,572 --> 01:54:29,494
So to sit there and publicly embarrass me, she's already called me racist many times.

1162
01:54:31,854 --> 01:54:32,874
And that's uncalled for.

1163
01:54:36,315 --> 01:54:41,896
So I will share with you the process as I met with many members of these organizations.

1164
01:54:43,937 --> 01:54:50,278
I would never ever, in the spirit of any of these ordinances, they're very good.

1165
01:54:51,328 --> 01:54:55,151
But as a city councilor, we have to weigh many different factors.

1166
01:54:57,052 --> 01:55:00,414
And because I've done that, I'm labeled a racist.

1167
01:55:02,916 --> 01:55:03,876
So shame on you, Ms.

1168
01:55:03,916 --> 01:55:04,257
Lerner.

1169
01:55:04,777 --> 01:55:07,799
I've given my life to this community and the people of this community.

1170
01:55:08,039 --> 01:55:11,021
