1173
01:55:22,356 --> 01:55:23,877
I mean, you had a minute left.

1174
01:55:24,297 --> 01:55:29,598
I'm going to go back to you if you'd like to finish your comment, but please direct your comments to the chair.

1175
01:55:31,178 --> 01:55:31,598
