1182
01:56:04,564 --> 01:56:06,045
That's all that's being asked.

1183
01:56:07,226 --> 01:56:15,871
Pledge yourself to finding the money instead of always saying, oh, no, we can't do this and we can't do that and we can't do the other thing.

1184
01:56:17,452 --> 01:56:18,813
Because maybe we can.

1185
01:56:18,833 --> 01:56:20,554
I think we can.

1186
01:56:21,897 --> 01:56:25,561
I'm optimistic, I love this town as much as you do, George.

1187
01:56:26,581 --> 01:56:31,466
You know, I think- Please direct your comments to the chair.

1188
01:56:31,746 --> 01:56:35,009
Please direct your comments to the chair.

1189
01:56:38,373 --> 01:56:42,837
Okay, that's, I mean, I don't feel like I need to have to defend myself.

