1586
02:35:57,495 --> 02:36:01,498
I wanted to write to explain the drug testing that transpired in December 9, 2024.

1587
02:36:02,179 --> 02:36:05,281
Testing protocol that took place at approximately 1230 p.m.

1588
02:36:05,341 --> 02:36:16,109
on Monday, December 9, 2024 was a result of the discovery of a hypodermic syringe on top of and inside the DPW men's locker room trash barrel earlier that morning by a union employee.

1589
02:36:16,943 --> 02:36:29,367
Not only was the discovery itself concerning, but the fact it was thrown into a regular trash barrel indicated that whoever had put it there was not educated in the proper disposal of sharps, and therefore it was unlikely to be a medically prescribed needle.

1590
02:36:30,408 --> 02:36:36,990
This was the latest example of a series of possible drug-related incidents to occur in the DPW over the past several months.

1591
02:36:37,770 --> 02:36:46,113
Just prior to the December 9 incident, it was reported that other drug paraphernalia had been discovered a week or two prior to in a DPW vehicle.

1592
02:36:47,170 --> 02:36:58,580
Additionally, there have been anonymous reporting from DPW employees to City Hall with claims and concerns of DPW employee drug use during work hours and the subsequent operation of City vehicles and equipment.

1593
02:36:59,981 --> 02:37:09,248
Due to the safety-sensitive nature of our work, operating heavy equipment and heavy-duty vehicles, there is an extreme risk to both employees and the public from workers being under the influence.

1594
02:37:10,071 --> 02:37:21,898
In fact, over the past nine months, there have been dozens of equipment and vehicle damage incidents, underscoring the need to be proactive in our oversight and management of employees, as well as the need to develop a more comprehensive internal policy.

1595
02:37:22,598 --> 02:37:27,561
We've also been contacted by our insurance broker due to their concern as it relates to accident volume.

1596
02:37:29,302 --> 02:37:38,148
